cc:Work.dc:title: HetzGNU
cc:Work.dc:description: This is a running GNU (in german language "hetzen", means something like beeing in a hurry or rush). Dorothea Dittberner has originally drawn this GNU for a hosting offer of her husband Jan.

cc:Agent.dc:title: Jan Dittberner scanned this image using the GIMP and XSane and vectorized it using Inkscape.p
